Once your payment and delivery pipeline is up and running, you can start scaling your business. This means increasing your revenue by creating more digital products and attracting more clients. To do this, you'll need to optimize your sales process and make it easier for your clients to pay and receive their digital products. This could involve creating a membership site or a subscription-based service that lets your clients access your digital products for a recurring fee. With the right tools and strategies in place, you can scale your business and reach new heights."
  ],
  "paa_response": "Your most likely question is, 'Will I be able to receive payments from clients in other countries?' The answer is yes – blockchain-based payments are global, and you can receive payments from clients anywhere in the world. You're not limited by traditional payment processors or their KYC regulations. This means you can focus on creating more digital products and growing your business, without worrying about being restricted by payment processors.
